  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年が明けて、一月三日の朝",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.5933335305
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "う～、やっぱり朝は寒いなぁ……。でも我慢我慢！",
      "startTime": 2.4666669529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日は遙子ちゃんより早く事務所に行かないと！",
      "startTime": 7.3000002783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshifacade-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshifacade-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.9935613316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何しろ遙子ちゃんの誕生日だもんね",
      "startTime": 11.9935613316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_start-04.m4a",
      "text": "事務所を飾り付けして、びっくりさせちゃうよ～",
      "startTime": 14.6417269842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-10.m4a",
      "text": "ハッピーバースデーの飾り付けを見たら",
      "startTime": 18.800455475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "きっと驚くだろうな。喜んでくれるといいな～",
      "startTime": 21.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.7506825132
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.7506825132
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_yes-02.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くんも早起きして飾り付けを",
      "startTime": 27.8006825132,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 27.4999988238
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "手伝ってくれる約束だけど、もう来てるかな？",
      "startTime": 30.6999995629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ、事務所に誰かいる。あの後ろ姿は",
      "startTime": 34.0609107656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-01.m4a",
      "text": "{user}くん……じゃない？",
      "startTime": 37.6666670722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.4078040443
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-02.m4a",
      "text": "あれは遙子ちゃんだ！　どうして先に来てるの！？",
      "startTime": 40.4078040443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "これじゃあ、サプライズ失敗だよ～",
      "startTime": 44.3333300829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshicorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshicorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.5746946338
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……仕方ない。せめて元気良くお祝いしよう！",
      "startTime": 47.5746946338,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "用意しておいたクラッカーを構えて……3、2、1",
      "startTime": 51.6666660549,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 133.3283184000038,
          "startTime": 51.7999943733
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5700.009409499998,
          "startTime": 57.3666754644
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6800.0094094999995,
          "startTime": 58.4666754644
        }
      ]
    },
    {
