    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あ……麻奈ちゃん……",
      "startTime": 67.3018278759,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-12.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃん？　その目……もしかして、泣いてたの？",
      "startTime": 70.5420545817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-11.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……それより、誕生日\nお祝いしてくれたのね。ありがとう。嬉しいわ……",
      "startTime": 80.3333474716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしたの？　何かあったの？",
      "startTime": 85.4977947474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私で良ければ話を聞くよ",
      "startTime": 88.5915245295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ついさっき、事務所に連絡があったの\nミュージカルのオーディションの結果が出たのよ",
      "startTime": 99.7666970809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "結果は不合格……\n私なりに頑張ってみたけど、ダメだったわ",
      "startTime": 106.1333637476,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sigh-01.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ……",
      "startTime": 109.3080352544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "残念だよ、あんなに頑張ってたのに……",
      "startTime": 111.5306269937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "セリフの練習で麻奈ちゃんに付き合ってもらったり\n夜遅くまで居残りで歌の練習をしたり……",
      "startTime": 118.8006373077,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "頑張ったおかげでオーディションでも上手に出来て\nこれはいけるかもって、手応えがあったのよ",
      "startTime": 125.7547821421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "きっとオーディションを突破出来る。麻奈ちゃんと\n一緒の舞台に立てる。そう期待してたのに……",
      "startTime": 132.566693012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、麻奈ちゃん\nせっかく練習に付き合ってくれたのに……",
      "startTime": 140.5000240565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_no-05.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに応援してくれたのに……\n期待に応えられなくてごめんね……",
      "startTime": 147.2000309229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "気にしないで。きっとこれからもチャンスはあるから",
      "startTime": 150.2701066414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その時にまた頑張れば……",
      "startTime": 155.2767814292,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "私って、どうしてこんなにダメなのかしら\nいつもみんなの期待を裏切って、がっかりさせて……",
      "startTime": 164.0000339745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_14_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "自分が情けないわ……\nやっぱり私なんて……",
      "startTime": 172.4666780789,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "遙子ちゃん……",
      "startTime": 176.198563059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "えいっ！",
      "startTime": 178.4005336795,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
